sub_title: Studying graphic design, looking for internship. Background in translations. Speaking 5 languages on a daily basis.
summary:
Studying Graphic design in Kraków, living in Rotterdam, and having a background in foreign languages and translation in Ukraine.

My big passion is creating concepts and identities and packaging design.

Speaking 5 languages: English, German, Polish, Ukrainian, and Russian. Learning Dutch.

I am looking for internship opportunities and junior roles in Graphic design.
